             <div class="mt-8 bg-white p-6 rounded-lg shadow-lg">
                <h3 class="font-display text-3xl text-center text-[#3D5A80] mb-2">NDA's Integrated Policy Ecosystem</h3>
                <p class="text-center text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-6">Unlike standalone policies of the past, the NDA's flagship programs were designed to work in synergy, creating a powerful, multi-faceted push for industrial growth and self-reliance.</p>
                <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-4">
                    <button class="policy-btn active w-full md:w-auto text-center bg-gray-200 text-[#293241] py-2 px-4 rounded-md font-semibold" onclick="showPolicy('mii')">'Make in India'</button>
                    <button class="policy-btn w-full md:w-auto text-center bg-gray-200 text-[#293241] py-2 px-4 rounded-md font-semibold" onclick="showPolicy('pli')">PLI Schemes</button>
